 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/umerauk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Merauk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Been around a while</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(7/26/01 10:08:06 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.elementofdarkness.com/images/member/Merauk/Kitty.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pickup group pro and con</span><hr size=1> I have done more then my fair share of pick up groups over the years (funny using the word years in this sentence).  For the most part I have never had a problem.  I still do experiance in Seb about once a month only in a pick up group.<br>
<br>
